What are the lengths of <m original-id="GT1-s3a2t2p1m1" internal-id="m-GT1-c-b-b-a-a">A\vec e_1</m> and <m original-id="GT1-s3a2t2p1m2" internal-id="m-GT1-c-b-b-a-b">A\vec e_2</m>?
