          <caption original-id="GT1-s3a3i1f2c2" internal-id="caption-GT1-c-c-a-b-b">Transformation of the unit square by the matrix <m original-id="GT1-s3a3i1f2c2m1" internal-id="m-GT1-c-c-a-b-b-a">B</m></caption>
        </figure>
        <p>
          <em>Part 1.</em>
        </p>
        <p original-id="GT1-s3a3t2p1" internal-id="p-GT1-c-c-b-a">
What are the lengths of <m original-id="GT1-s3a3t2p1m1" internal-id="m-GT1-c-c-b-a-a">B\vec e_1</m> and <m original-id="GT1-s3a3t2p1m2" internal-id="m-GT1-c-c-b-a-b">B\vec e_2</m>?
        </p>
